One of the leaders of Coalition for Revolution, CORE, also known as #Revolutionnow, Pelumi Olajengbesin, addressing newsmen on behalf of the protesters, on Wednesday morning. Olajengbesin demanded a drastic change in Nigeria’s political leadership and also an alleged failure of the Buhari-led administration following poor performance and lack of direction. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-1437251" src="https://i2.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG-20200805-WA0000.jpg?resize=600%2C800&#038;ssl=1" alt="Photos, video of Revolutionnow​ protest in Abuja" width="600" height="800" srcset="https://i2.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG-20200805-WA0000.jpg?w=756&amp;ssl=1 756w, https://i2.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG-20200805-WA0000.jpg?resize=225%2C300&amp;ssl=1 225w, https://i2.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG-20200805-WA0000.jpg?resize=44%2C58&amp;ssl=1 44w, https://i2.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG-20200805-WA0000.jpg?resize=146%2C194&amp;ssl=1 146w, https://i2.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG-20200805-WA0000.jpg?resize=98%2C130&amp;ssl=1 98w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" data-recalc-dims="1" /> <img class="aligncenter wp-image-1437253" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG-20200805-WA0001.jpg?resize=600%2C800&#038;ssl=1" alt="Photos, video of Revolutionnow​ protest in Abuja" width="600" height="800" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG-20200805-WA0001.jpg?w=768&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG-20200805-WA0001.jpg?resize=225%2C300&amp;ssl=1 225w, https://i0.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG-20200805-WA0001.jpg?resize=44%2C58&amp;ssl=1 44w, https://i0.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG-20200805-WA0001.jpg?resize=146%2C194&amp;ssl=1 146w, htt